OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government does not want Sats tests
OL,6, to be "too hard for children",         
OL,7, England's schools minister has said -  
OL,8, after claims a Year 6 reading paper was
OL,9, so difficult it left pupils in tears.  
OL,11,FNick Gibb said the assessments had to  
OL,12,F"test a range of ability" but he would 
OL,13,Flook at the paper because of the       
OL,14,Fconcerns.                              
OL,16,FHe said he looked at the tests each    
OL,17,Fyear once they were publicly available.
OL,19,FThere is no suggestion there will be   
OL,20,Fany kind of formal review.             
